-- Bombardier to Expand Global Aircraft Family With Announcement Next Month
-- B y   J o A n n e   N o r t o n
-- 2010-09-30T11:39:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/bombardier-to-expand-global-aircraft-family-with-announcement-next-month.html
Bombardier Inc.’s Bombardier
Aerospace said today its board has approved an “expanded Global
aircraft family.” The company will disclose details on Oct. 18.  The Global aircraft family will build on Bombardier’s
Global 5000 and Global Express XRS large business jet aircraft.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
JoAnne Norton at 
 jnorton@bloomberg.net  